name: forlovedao
description: For love, dao can provide everyone with the opportunity to live alone with the actresses they yearn for. The project issues its own tokens, establishes a treasury, locks 50% of the raised amount, and waits for the community to vote to decide how to use it. The rest of the currency is used as Circulation, you can shoot a certain actress's exclusive nft, and later projects can empower her. You can use nft to travel with the goddess you yearn for. The specific travel time is determined by community voting. For love, everyone has the opportunity to get along with the goddess and make the world full of love.
